{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Embark on a Neon Moon Odyssey</strong></h2>Begin your adventure in Neon Moon, a Metroidvania world brimming with secrets, powers, and ancient lore. Stand as the beacon of light against the Dark Night that shrouds Nightlight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/gif_1.gif?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Nightlight</strong></h2>Uncover the mysteries of a world rich in hidden paths and characters. Your journey will reveal the interconnectedness of an expansive and evocative setting.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/gif_7.gif?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Master Your Abilities</strong></h2>Harness the powers of fireflies, craft tools to enhance your exploration, and master your combat skills to navigate through the challenges that await in Nightlight.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/gif_3.gif?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Craft and Conquer</strong></h2>Outwit foes with crafted items and traps. Confront the legendary adversaries of Nightlight and emerge victorious, using their essence to forge powerful weapons.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/gif_6.gif?t=1717715965\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/extras/section_spacer.png?t=1717715965\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engage in a rich, side-scrolling action adventure where agility and skill are your greatest weapons.<br></li><li>Harness the mystical powers of fireflies for a dynamic combat experience with a variety of abilities.<br></li><li>Strategic gameplay: Craft tools and items, set traps, and use buffs to outsmart your enemies.<br></li><li>Confront and conquer formidable foes to absorb their power and expand your arsenal.<br></li><li>Explore the depths of Nightlight, a beautifully hand-drawn world filled with intricate paths, hidden secrets, and characters.<br></li><li>Forge your own path, make impactful choices, and write your own legend in the world of Neon Moon.<br></li><li>Unlock new abilities and customize your playstyle to face unique challenges.<br></li><li>Immerse yourself in an atmospheric world with a hauntingly beautiful soundtrack.<br></li><li>Engage in challenging side quests that enrich your journey and lead to unexpected treasures.<br></li><li>Experience a deep narrative that intertwines the fate of multiple characters with your own destiny.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717715965"